To say. "I love you." right out loud

1378
01:40:57.940 --> 01:41:03.189
Dreams and schemes and circus crowds

1379
01:41:04.189 --> 01:41:09.189
I've looked at life that way

1380
01:41:09.981 --> 01:41:14.648
But now old friends
They're acting strange

1381
01:41:14.731 --> 01:41:20.231
They shake their heads
They say I've changed

1382
01:41:20.314 --> 01:41:26.606
Well. something's lost
But something's gained

1383
01:41:26.689 --> 01:41:31.147
In living every day

1384
01:41:31.231 --> 01:41:37.065
I've looked at life
From both sides now

1385
01:41:37.147 --> 01:41:42.690
From win and lose. and still somehow

1386
01:41:42.773 --> 01:41:48.147
It's life's illusions I recall

1387
01:41:48.231 --> 01:41:54.231
I really don't know life

1388
01:41:55.981 --> 01:42:02.272
I've looked at life
From both sides now

1389
01:42:02.356 --> 01:42:07.314
From up and down. and still somehow

1390
01:42:07.398 --> 01:42:13.439
It's life's illusions I recall

1391
01:42:13.523 --> 01:42:18.189
I really don't know life

1392
